    <item>
      <title>中东油价上涨，交易商入市数量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/rally-in-middle-east-oil-has-traders-piling-in-at-record-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油交易商持有的一份合约达到了创纪录的持仓量，该合约允许他们押注中东原油和全球布伦特基准原油之间的价格差异，这凸显出对俄罗斯出口实施前所未有的制裁正在如何撼动原油流通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/rally-in-middle-east-oil-has-traders-piling-in-at-record-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 12:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
