      <title>欧洲债券偿还导致突尼斯外汇储备缩水 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/eurobond-payment-shrinks-tunisia-s-forex-reserves-by-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于资金紧张的突尼斯政府继续利用央行来偿还债务，该国的外汇储备在一天之内下降了近 13%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/eurobond-payment-shrinks-tunisia-s-forex-reserves-by-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 12:03:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
